            <p ana="start" loc="novel1_letter4_chapter16_p473"/>These <seg xml:id="C23_app782-f1823_end"/>were wild and miserable <seg xml:id="C23_app784-f1823_start"/>thoughts; <seg xml:id="C23_app784-f1823_end"/>but I cannot describe to you how the eternal twinkling of <seg type="invariant-MissingWit" xml:id="C23_app788-f1823_start"/>the <seg xml:id="C23_app788-f1823_end"/>stars weighed upon me, and <seg type="invariant-MissingWit" xml:id="C23_app792-f1823_start"/>how <seg xml:id="C23_app792-f1823_end"/>I listened to every blast of <seg xml:id="C23_app794-f1823_start"/>wind, <seg xml:id="C23_app794-f1823_end"/>as <seg type="invariant-MissingWit" xml:id="C23_app796-f1823_start"/>if <seg xml:id="C23_app796-f1823_end"/>it were a dull ugly <seg xml:id="C23_app798-f1823_start"/>siroc <seg xml:id="C23_app798-f1823_end"/>on its way to consume <seg xml:id="C23_app802-f1823_start"/>me.<p ana="end" loc="novel1_letter4_chapter16_p473"/>
